1219
00:45:48,220 --> 00:45:50,080
or two,

1220
00:45:50,080 --> 00:45:50,540
or three,

1221
00:45:50,680 --> 00:45:53,220
you know that the laws of physics are not symmetric

1222
00:45:53,220 --> 00:45:54,980
