1652
01:03:39,760 --> 01:03:41,020
that this number

1653
01:03:41,020 --> 01:03:43,560
is 10 to the minus eighth

1654
01:03:45,020 --> 01:03:47,420
times NQ plus NQ bar.

1655
01:03:47,720 --> 01:03:48,080
Oops.

1656
01:03:49,460 --> 01:03:50,580
That's out of range.

1657
01:03:50,880 --> 01:03:52,040
We don't know how to do that.

1658
01:03:52,040 --> 01:03:55,300
That's the status of this particular problem.

1659
01:03:55,740 --> 01:03:56,640
As I said,

1660
01:03:56,640 --> 01:03:57,660
it's called baryogenesis.

1661
01:04:01,500 --> 01:04:04,840
And it will await

1662
01:04:04,840 --> 01:04:08,920
a much more detailed theory

1663
01:04:08,920 --> 01:04:10,980
of both early cosmology

1664
01:04:10,980 --> 01:04:15,420
and particle physics at very high energy.

1665
01:04:15,640 --> 01:04:16,700
Any questions about that?

1666
01:04:17,140 --> 01:04:19,260
We are now finished with baryogenesis.

1667
01:04:20,160 --> 01:04:21,980
But the fact that we know

1668
01:04:21,980 --> 01:04:23,540
that we have a measurement

1669
01:04:23,540 --> 01:04:25,100
of 10 to the minus eighth,

1670
01:04:25,900 --> 01:04:27,720
I imagine that puts some constraints

1671
01:04:27,720 --> 01:04:29,160
on what these theories could look like.

1672
01:04:29,280 --> 01:04:29,580
It does.

1673
01:04:29,960 --> 01:04:30,600
It does.

1674
01:04:31,020 --> 01:04:31,680
It does.

