01:04:32,980 --> 01:04:33,780
Another question.

1676
01:04:34,900 --> 01:04:35,780
It does,

1677
01:04:35,780 --> 01:04:36,900
but they're hard to use.

1678
01:04:37,900 --> 01:04:38,580
You're right,

1679
01:04:38,580 --> 01:04:40,720
but to my knowledge,

1680
01:04:40,760 --> 01:04:42,600
nobody's used it in a really effective way

1681
01:04:42,600 --> 01:04:43,660
