To map out a neat-looking subspace.

1685
01:04:47,720 --> 01:04:48,020
Yeah,

1686
01:04:48,020 --> 01:04:49,360
right.

1687
01:04:49,840 --> 01:04:51,160
Of hundreds of parameters,

1688
01:04:51,160 --> 01:04:52,580
we just don't know enough.

1689
01:04:52,720 --> 01:04:52,920
Yeah.

