3118
01:53:02,180 --> 01:53:05,360
It might roll down the hill in a few seconds.

3119
01:53:05,680 --> 01:53:06,020
All right?

3120
01:53:06,240 --> 01:53:07,620
With a large friction,

3121
01:53:07,840 --> 01:53:09,800
it could take years to roll down the hill,

3122
01:53:09,860 --> 01:53:11,480
depending on the magnitude of the friction.

3123
01:53:12,279 --> 01:53:15,300
So this is called the cosmic friction term.

3124
01:53:15,300 --> 01:53:19,120
In the equation of motion of a scalar field.

3125
01:53:19,680 --> 01:53:21,200
And it has the effect,

3126
01:53:21,260 --> 01:53:23,800
it has the simple effect of slowing down

3127
01:53:23,800 --> 01:53:25,460
the evolution of the system

3128
01:53:25,460 --> 01:53:30,400
and keeping the ball from rolling down the hill.

3129
01:53:30,840 --> 01:53:31,920
The next time,

3130
01:53:31,940 --> 01:53:33,400
